pro_course_detail.description:
Lessons are based on the Cutting Edge book. For example, we have a new topic "Everyday life":
1) we learn new vocabulary;
2) read dialogue to use a new language in a real-life situation;
3) unpack a grammar structure used in the dialogue;
4) switch to a Phonics section and learn new phonics;
5) read a text full of fun facts on the topic;
